text: The 2018 Wayne State Warriors football team represented Wayne State University in the 2018 NCAA Division II football season. They were led by 15th year head coach Paul Winters and played their home games at Tom Adams Field. They finished the 2018 season with a losing record of 2–9 in the Great Lakes Intercollegiate Athletic Conference. == Schedule == ==References== Wayne State Category:Wayne State Warriors football seasons Wayne State
